snippet.textDisplay:
Leg kicks, takedowns, defensive checks, octagon control - Jon.

Strikes - slight edge to reyes.


Throwing more punches does not equal a win in MMA, nor does landing more punches. This isn't boxing. Add in the fact a good majority of those strikes were blocked and just sounded loud because he was smacking his gloves and arms. Dude did nothing be solidify the inevitable. He gassed himself and literally fought like a wounded animal for 2 and a half rounds, including the FINAL round. Champs don't get walked down like that in the last 2 rounds. There was literally nothing he could do once he gassed. Jones started punishing him halway through the 3rd and the judges noticed it too.
